dc_description_s: 1 map ; 36 x 47 cm.|Relief shown pictorially.|Decorative cartouche with cherubims holding a coat of arms and musical scale bars in upper left of map. Includes an illustration of Neptune holding a shell around the map title.|This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637, and 1680.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
